data.description: Beautiful Custom home fully fenced on 3 acres with remote or coded electrical gated entrance. 4 bedroom home with spacious rooms. Home boast a bonus room which can act as an office, den, or possible 5th bedroom. Great room with fireplace and giant picturesque windows of the surrounding views. Kitchen has knotty alder cabinets, double wall oven, new gas range, microwave and dishwasher. Kitchen also has breakfast bar, and a large dining room. Master Bedroom boast a spacious bathroom with garden tub, walk in shower, walk in closets and private toilet room. Sit out back or hosts guest on the beautiful back covered patio and enjoy the mature landscaping with trees and lawn and surrounding mountain views. More pics coming soon or can find on history search of property.2 yr old interior paint
